posts.post_title: ATTN T205 Set Builders: VG-EX ($30); VG ($25); & GD ($21) Common Sale
posts.post_content:
I am selling off a large portion of my T205s.  Email [url]vettejayk@aol.com[/url] to get scans of a particular grouping.  

This FS page is for GD, VG, and VG-EX commons.  No back damage or writing, but can have a crease or corner rounding.

Shipping is included in a plain white envelope.  Can offer some discounts on a bigger grouping.
